{
  "stem": "734.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I went wild with that camera, took everything and everything that-- [LAUGHS].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And this is how, slowly and surely, I decided to become a photographer.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then Mr.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Orenstein, being a, a friend of the family, gave me an idea.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Why don't I go into someplace after school and see how people-- learn how pe-- how to process film.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because processing film was very expensive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I didn't have that much money to, you know-- my allowance was meager.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then I had to earn money by doing, doing errands for my relatives.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I didn't have that much time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Because I had to study the violin and lots, lots of homework, and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I decided to learn that maybe I could do it myself one day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Orenstein allowed me to come in occasionally, like twice a week or so, to the studio and watch the people in the dark room.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And this is how I learned how to process film.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And eventually, I did process my own film.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he allowed me to come in there when it will be all, like, late afternoon, when everything would be quiet.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I could process my own film in the darkroom.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "So this is how-- this is exactly how I got hooked in photography.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And then when the war broke out, I already knew, more or less, how to make a print, how to process film.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Orenstein was gone.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When the Nazis came into Radom, he was gone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "He went east, because he was afraid that they might take they might him for some reason or what.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
